headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The Doomsday Heist Challenge
content:
Unite with the GTA Online community against the threat of total annihilation and conquer Act III of The Doomsday Heist – The Doomsday Scenario – for a cumulative take of over GTA$100,000,000,000 by November 22 to unlock a new livery for the legendary Pegassi Zentorno (Super, 50% off) later this year.

Plus, get Double GTA$ and RP on The Doomsday Scenario Finale, as well as in all Prep Missions.
